## Generative Loop Summary

1. Parse constraints  
2. Build design space  
3. Initialize candidate population  
4. Evaluate (fast → mid → high fidelity)  
5. Score and prune  
6. Mutate and recombine  
7. Converge on viable candidates  
8. Output top structures with predicted properties  

